1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:01,751
With this he whipped me

2
00:00:02,584 --> 00:00:05,667
Not exactly this one, he also whipped me with a water hose

3
00:00:07,334 --> 00:00:10,334
Interviewer: When you see these things in the street?

4
00:00:10,542 --> 00:00:16,751
Yes, I immediately remember that I was tortured with them

5
00:00:20,500 --> 00:00:27,584
One time he whipped me with a bamboo stick

6
00:00:29,459 --> 00:00:34,209
Once I was whipped with a water hose that made a sound

7
00:00:35,250 --> 00:00:38,167
And I was also whipped with something like an electric cable

8
00:00:39,292 --> 00:00:40,792
Do you see this hose

9
00:00:44,167 --> 00:00:49,876
With a hose like this he whipped me

10
00:00:50,584 --> 00:00:54,918
He also whipped me with the stick and it left marks on my body

11
00:00:55,459 --> 00:00:57,542
And the other time the electric cable was harsher

12
00:00:59,751 --> 00:01:04,751
The cable strikes harder, not like the hose or the stick which are lighter

13
00:01:05,709 --> 00:01:10,209
The cable hurts more in torture

14
00:01:10,918 --> 00:01:12,375
Its strike is harsher

15
00:01:13,542 --> 00:01:14,751
And the pain is stronger

16
00:01:16,167 --> 00:01:21,959
Because it is heavy, maybe it weighs 10 kilograms

17
00:01:22,626 --> 00:01:25,500
Or five kilograms, or two kilograms

18
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:29,125
The strike of the cable hurts more

19
00:01:29,959 --> 00:01:34,209
So imagine if it was 20 lashes, how would you feel

20
00:01:35,834 --> 00:01:39,542
You need to know that when he hits you

21
00:01:40,209 --> 00:01:46,167
He counts two or three times until seven if you don’t scream

22
00:01:47,250 --> 00:01:50,626
And if you remain silent without screaming from the pain

23
00:01:51,334 --> 00:01:56,876
If he was hitting lightly, he increases the force so you scream

24
00:01:58,584 --> 00:02:03,876
I swear to God when they gave me 20 lashes I didn’t scream

25
00:02:04,667 --> 00:02:06,667
He asked me, Didn’t it hurt? I said, Yes

26
00:02:07,459 --> 00:02:10,334
He said, Why didn’t you scream? I told him, I’m not a woman to scream

27
00:02:12,542 --> 00:02:15,542
So he said to them, Take him back to the
prison, meaning he wanted to release me

28
00:02:17,167 --> 00:02:19,459
He was supposed to release me, but he sent me back to prison

29
00:02:21,834 --> 00:02:25,167
Because I didn’t scream from the pain

30
00:02:26,667 --> 00:02:30,125
Many people screamed because of the pain

31
00:02:31,334 --> 00:02:36,459
Of course the one who couldn’t handle it screamed

32
00:02:37,083 --> 00:02:39,542
And the one who endured the whipping got beaten harder

33
00:02:41,876 --> 00:02:45,542
Interviewer: Is this the story you remember most?

34
00:02:45,834 --> 00:02:49,250
Yes this is what I remember most from the torture

35
00:02:50,459 --> 00:02:52,959
Especially when he tortured me with 20 lashes

36
00:02:53,959 --> 00:02:59,250
Because I endured the beating and didn’t scream

37
00:03:01,292 --> 00:03:03,459
He sent me back to prison again and didn’t release me

38
00:03:04,792 --> 00:03:06,000
That’s what I remember most

39
00:03:06,584 --> 00:03:10,584
He was supposed to whip me 10 lashes and release me

40
00:03:11,334 --> 00:03:13,834
But he continued to 20 lashes and said, Go back to prison

41
00:03:15,209 --> 00:03:20,375
Knowing there could be someone older or younger than him

42
00:03:20,667 --> 00:03:22,584
As you know my eyes were blindfolded

43
00:03:23,042 --> 00:03:24,542
But the one who was questioning me

44
00:03:25,417 --> 00:03:29,667
I think he was sitting at a table or something

45
00:03:29,918 --> 00:03:31,292
I don’t know because my eyes were blindfolded

46
00:03:31,709 --> 00:03:33,834
He said, Whip him 10 lashes and release him

47
00:03:35,083 --> 00:03:37,292
But he whipped me 20 lashes and sent me back

48
00:03:39,959 --> 00:03:43,167
That’s how it was, and it affected me the most

49
00:03:52,834 --> 00:03:56,918
Interviewer: In the end, would you like to add something?

50
00:03:57,042 --> 00:03:59,959
Or mention something you haven’t yet?

51
00:04:00,584 --> 00:04:02,918
I wish I couldn’t remember anything

52
00:04:03,250 --> 00:04:07,125
Interviewer: Why?
Witness: Because I want to forget them

53
00:04:08,459 --> 00:04:13,876
Because while I’m talking about all this I speak as if I’m living it

54
00:04:14,792 --> 00:04:18,500
Like I’m living the event in this moment

55
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:22,667
I want to forget, that’s better for me
